00:18:43.166 --> 00:18:45.335
Pergilah ke Pulau Morang.

00:18:45.418 --> 00:18:46.419
Pak?

00:18:47.379 --> 00:18:49.756
Tapi aku mabuk laut parah.

00:18:50.340 --> 00:18:51.925
Bacakan tabel perkalian. Itu ampuh.

00:18:52.801 --> 00:18:54.403
Dua dikali satu dua, dua dikali dua empat.

00:18:54.427 --> 00:18:55.762
- Dua dikali enam?
- Dua belas.

00:18:56.555 --> 00:18:58.116
- Enam dikali delapan?
- Empat puluh delapan.

00:18:58.140 --> 00:18:59.474
Bagus. Lakukan saja itu di kapal.

00:18:59.558 --> 00:19:01.977
Park Yeonghan dan Kim Sangsun!
Ke mana mereka pergi?

00:19:02.978 --> 00:19:03.979
Menyebar! Sana!

00:19:04.062 --> 00:19:05.897
- Biar kutangani ini. Ayo, cepat.
- Sial.

00:19:05.981 --> 00:19:07.649
Cepat!

00:19:08.441 --> 00:19:09.442
Cepatlah.

00:19:09.526 --> 00:19:11.069
Astaga, ke mana mereka…

00:19:11.153 --> 00:19:13.572
Apa? Apa itu? Hei!

00:19:13.655 --> 00:19:17.325
"Bukankah ada kucing besar di sana?"

00:19:17.409 --> 00:19:20.203
- "Bukankah ada…
